<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENBP70A2406003" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Wheel Inspection
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A2406003001">
<title>
Visual Inspection
</title>
<ptxt>
Inspect wheels for cracks, bends, dents, wheel nut hole deformation or other damages.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Replace any wheel with defect(s).
</ptxt>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A2406003002">
<title>
Wheel Runout Inspection
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install wheel (either with or without tire) on wheel balancer or other appropriate equipment.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Set dial gage applying its plunger to wheel at angles “a” and “b” as shown in figure.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Give wheel a full turn slowly and record the maximum dial gauge reading for each of the angle “a” (lateral runout) measurement and the angle “b” (radial runout) measurement.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Replace wheel if either or both of the recorded dial gauge readings exceed the following limits.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<spec>
<title>
Wheel runout
</title>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
